https://gruntjs.com/
https://gruntjs.com/plugins
https://gruntjs.com/getting-started

--- configuração ---
node js
npm init //para criar o arquivo package.js
npm install -g grunt-cli
npm install grunt --save-dev


--- comandos grunt ---
grunt --version

----- gruntfile.js -----
* grunt.initConfig
Fica a configuração de cada plugin.


* grunt.registerTask

--- executar sem intalar globalmente --
./node_modules/grunt/bin/grunt --version
./node_modules/grunt/bin/grunt build  // faz build do projeto

